==English==
===Etymology===
[[clip]] + [[board]]

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#<!--DefA--> A flat piece of [[rigid]] material, such as card or plastic, with a clip at one end under which papers can be held.
#<!--DefB-->{{computing}} A [[buffer]] in [[memory]] where the [[user]] can [[store]] [[data]] [[temporarily]] while [[transfer]]ring it from one place within an [[application]] to another or between applications.

